{"tid":12319,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓梓亮 感謝粉絲 不離不棄搞歌迷聚會","createTime":"2016-11-29T15:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T04:13:44.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"081d3227439366ae5b11f27df5dc4cac74c0902b","tid":12319,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:08:20.000Z","msg":"歌手韓梓亮（MAX.B）為慶祝出道10個月特別舉行歌迷聚會，有約20名歌迷出席，他表示非常開心，因自己不是有名氣偶像，故事前不知可會有歌迷到場，他連聲道謝說：「感謝歌迷一直對我不離不棄，一直支持我同守護我。」 <br />\n<br />\nMAX.B又謂曾經在網上有人留言攻擊他，但其歌迷即時在網上維護他，不停留言反擊攻擊者，令他受寵若驚，又說以往曾遭過不少網絡欺凌，有感網上駁火、對罵不是最佳解決問題方法，故唯有啞忍及自我反省，他說：「我覺得最好嘅解決方法，係自己繼續努力，做好自己，用音樂去證明自己。」 <br />\n<br />\n問到MAX.B將踏入新一年有何新願望，他表示：「嚟緊都係注重訓練，增值自己，稍後會跟吳浩學唱歌，又會不停學跳舞進修自己。」現時他已經錄好兩首歌，迄下正進入排舞階段，而新歌風格構思來自歐美style。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20161128/bkn-20161128025022365-1128_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20161128%2Fbkn-20161128025022365-1128_00862_001.html&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyYscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=5c3d6f95\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20161128/bkn-20161128025022365-1128_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7c1b940e657bfa8837171b19001542498bba4e86","tid":12319,"uid":18040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"邊個黎"},{"pid":"5c7f38a99c2f0f68bd02e2d74dab3bba452f568e","tid":12319,"uid":6860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:10:34.000Z","msg":"聽都未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa6b28720814515fd512877acda3bb55060361e","tid":12319,"uid":16029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:11:57.000Z","msg":"Max b<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkg